title: Conselho Distrital de Agricultura
body: It was created by decree on December 24, 1901, and held its first session (the installation session) on July 16, 1904, and its last on August 1, 1910. This Council, which was especially concerned with the agricultural development of the Madeira region, was abolished by article 289 of the Law of July 9, 1913.
